			<description><![CDATA[<h2>
Come help Lullabot build the biggest and best Drupal websites in existence.</h2>
<p>
Lullabot is expanding its development team and looking for a few amazing Drupal developers. We&#39;ve got several projects in the works with some really great high-profile clients. If you feel that you have distinguished yourself as a superior Drupal developer and would like to work with Lullabot&#39;s excellent team, please fill out the form below and tell us about yourself and your areas of expertise.</p>
<p>
<strong>Ideal candidates will ...</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Be familiar with Lullabot and have extensive experience in Drupal and the Drupal community</li>
<li>
Be able to display 2+ years of in-depth experience with high-performance Drupal sites</li>
<li>
Be self-directed and able to effectively manage their own tasks</li>
<li>
Be a great writer and communicator</li>
<li>
Be familiar with SVN and Git and Drupal development technologies such as Drush, Features, and Context</li>
<li>
Have a well-rounded knowledge of Drupal-adjunct technologies such as the LAMP platform, HTML5, CSS3, jQuery/JavaScript</li>
<li>
Be quick-witted with a good sense of humor</li>
</ul>
<p>
Pay will be commensurate with experience.</p>
<p>
<strong>Extra credit</strong></p>
<p>
Create a brief (2 min or less) video introducing yourself and talking about your interest and experience for this job. We recommend creating a password protected video on Vimeo, but you certainly post your video wherever/however you&#39;d like.&nbsp;Take a look at <a href="http://vimeo.com/21191319">one</a>-<a href="http://vimeo.com/26632559">of</a>-<a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fC4pL193fVw">these</a>-<a href="http://dl.dropbox.com/u/1771736/Video/James%20Sansbury.m4v">videos</a> to see what&#39;s gotten folks hired in the past.</p>
<p>
<strong>About Lullabot</strong></p>
<p>
Lullabot is a distributed company with flexible hours, but we tend to schedule meetings and expect employees to be on-line and available during a North American workday. Our current team is spread out across North America and Europe.&nbsp;Lullabot&#39;s past clients include Sony Music, FastCompany, The Grammys, MTV UK, O&#39;Reilly Media, Lifetime Television, and many more.</p>
<p>
Working for Lullabot is probably unlike anything you&rsquo;ve done before. To slightly paraphrase Voltaire (and Stan Lee!), &ldquo;With great freedom comes great responsibility.&rdquo; At Lullabot, you get to (generally) make your own hours and work from home or wherever you like. Self-direction, a casual but confident attitude, and a focus on quality over quantity are some of the things we look for. We work from both the head and the heart and guide our decisions by our <a href="http://www.lullabot.com/values">Core Values</a>.</p>
]]></description>
